Flow control describe the order in which the statement will be executed at runtime.





			Flow-Control
			    |
			    |
         ---------------------------------------------------------------	
         |				|				|
1.Selection Statement	  2.Iterative Statement			3.Transfer Statement	


1.if-else		1.while()				1.break
2.switch()		2.do-while()				2.Continue
			3.for()					3.return 
			4.for-each loop(1.5v)			4.try-catch-finally
								5.assert(1.4v)

